\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1\ul\b\f0\fs22\lang9 Task 1\par
\ulnone\b0\par
1. \ldblquote Forgot password\rdblquote  email is not being sent for the user account.\par
\b Priority: Urgent\par
\b0 The \ldblquote Forgot password\rdblquote  email is not being sent,  preventing existing users who have forgotten their passwords from accessing their accounts.It is a common human error to forget a password and tis should always be taken into consideration with any software that uses login forms to interact with its customers. It is a critical usability issue that locks users out of the accounts which makes it impossible for them to have account access. It can cause frustration on the user's part and some may even leave to competitors if this type of issue persists so resolving this issue is vital for access of users.\par
2. Website language switcher is not working.\par
\b Priority: High\par
\b0 Given that this is a subscription service catering to an international market, not being able to switch languages significantly can cause problematic for  accessibility for a large portion of your potential user base. This directly impacts user experience and could prevent many international users from fully engaging with the website and subscribing.\par
If it were not for an international market the priority would be low as users will likely still be able to use the website in the default language. It may hinder accesibility for some but would not prevent basic functionality for everyone.\par
\par
3. \ldblquote About-us\rdblquote  footer links are redirecting to the homepage.\par
\b Priority: Low\par
\b0 Incorrect links are not desirable and should always be fixed,but they don't directly prevent users from subscribing or using the core functionality of the service, which is the bottom line. The "About Us" page is typically informational, giving a background about the company,  and less critical to the immediate user journey of subscribing and using the service.. Users can likely still navigate to the "About Us" information through other means like through the main navigation.\par
4. During registration month date-of-birth dropdown box is only showing \ldblquote November\rdblquote .\par
\b Priority: High\par
\b0 During registration month date-of-birth dropdown box is only showing \ldblquote November\rdblquote : While users might eventually figure out a workaround (if possible), this is a major usability flaw during a critical onboarding process. It  can lead to incorrect data entry, potentially causing issues later with date of birth features or compliance.This directly impacts the acquisition of new subscribers.\par
5. \ldblquote Complete registration\rdblquote  button not working.\par
\b Priority: Urgent\par
\b0 "Complete registration" button not working: This is a a very urgent issue which needs to be addressed as soon as possible. If new users cannot finish signing up for the service, te renders  the entire subscription model unusable for them. There is a risk of losing potential customers.\par
\ul\b Task 2\par
\ulnone\b0 Below I havelisted the considerations to be taken into account as part of the test planning process:\ul\b\par
\ulnone Functionality & Requirements:\par
\b0 Voucher Generation:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Voucher Generation Logic: How are vouchers generated? (e.g., sequential, random, with specific patterns). Will they be generated using randomization for unique numbers, sequential generation and /or using specific patterns.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Bulk Generation: Does the system support generating large batches of vouchers? Perfomance and scalanility will need to be tested here\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Customization: Can vouchers have specific attributes such as expiry dates, usage limits, daily limits, specific product, discount amounts, discount percentages, reward points system\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Voucher Redemption:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Redemption Validation: Testing how the system validates a voucher. This can be done by checking for existence, expiry, usage limits, applicability,and other types of validation tests\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Redemption Methods: Involves testing how the vouchers can be redeemed  like online input, scanning a QR code, in-store entry, purchasing from a banking app.Also checking whether partial redemption is possible and having the balance remain on the customer's account\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Redemption Errors: How does the system handle invalid or expired vouchers? Clear, concise and informative error messages are important.\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Voucher Management:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Voucher Status Tracking: How is the status of a voucher tracked (e.g., active, redeemed, expired, cancelled)? We need to verify status updates.\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Voucher Cancellation/Invalidation: Does the system allow for the cancellation or invalidation of vouchers? Also need to test it's impact on voucher redemption\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Voucher Information : Can administrators easily search for and view details of specific vouchers? Testing search functionality and data accuracy is important.\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Performance:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Generation Speed: How quickly can vouchers be generated, especially in bulk? Load testing might be required.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Redemption Speed: Tests how quickly  vouchers are validated and processed during redemption. This under extreme loads\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}System Responsiveness: Tests the responsive of the administrative interface for managing vouchers\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Usability:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 User-Friendliness: Is the interface for managing vouchers intuitive and easy to use for administrators? \par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Customer Redemption Process: Is the voucher redemption process seamless,  clear and straightforward for customers?\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Reliability:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 System Stability: Is the system stable and can it handle  and maintainexpected loads without crashing or data loss?\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Data Integrity: Is the voucher data accurate and consistent throughout the system lifecycle?\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Scalability:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Load Testing: Can the system handle a significant increase in the number of vouchers generated and redeemed as the service grows? \par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Maintainability:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Troubleshooting : Is there troubleshooting assistance available for users in the case of common errors and is this constantly updated?\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Language and Currency Support: If vouchers involve monetary value, does the system support multiple currencies? Consider whether the system supports various currencies and languages or whether it is specific only to the country's currency with various languages, and testing this.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Date and Time Formats: Are date and time formats handled correctly for different locales?\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Which payment methods can be used to puchase vouchers?eg. eft, paypal, instant money, etc\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Security:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl240\slmult1 Voucher Code Security: Testing how secure  the generated voucher codes are against fraud, guessing or manipulation? Penetration testing will be helpfull here\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Redemption Security: Is the redemption process secure to prevent fraudulent use?\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Data Security: How is sensitive voucher data protected.Personal details of users.Consideration of the POPI act and other leagal compliance implications.\par

